hopobject.body: Not available at the moment cost for staxyn Any holidaymakers due to visit the country who do want to cancel or rearrange their trips will not be able to do so free of charge. All those tour operators contacted by Telegraph Travel - except Abercrombie and Kent, which said it would look at requests on a case-by-case basis - confirmed that “normal booking conditions” would apply unless the Foreign Office chose to issue a complete warning against travel to Kenya.
